                            <comment id="89541" author="ulsa" created="Sat, 20 Apr 2013 13:06:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I agree, it&apos;s wrong to bundle a log4j.properties in src/main. I&apos;m considering just moving the file to src/test/resources instead. Would that cause any other trouble?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
